data.description: This Stunning 3 bed, 2 bath home in the desirable neighborhood of Northgate in Homestead. Situated on a large corner lot and a double lot, with over 13000 square feet. This home has plenty of natural light, and screened patios on the front and back of the property for extra entertaining and living space. 2 car garage and 4 parking spaces in front of the home. Kitchen was remodeled and all new smart Samsung appliances 1 year ago. New flooring throughout entire home. Club house and resort style amenities: pool and jacuzzi hot tub, sauna with a gym, library, billiards room and ping pong room. The association includes weekly maintenance of all landscaping. High speed internet and cable. Roaming security and manned gate 24 hrs 7 days a week and alarm. Association paints the home every 7 years
